projects.name: XXonBoard
projects.description: It is well known that women are not well represented on executive boards. This project is a way to use coding practices (web scraping, python, natural language processing) to have a visually pleasing representation of the gender disparity.

projects.name: CSF Simon Says
projects.description: The Cybersecurity Framework logo already looks like the game 'Simon' so why not make it so & teach folks about the CSF while we're at it!
